<p>Eccentric fashion designer Dame Zandra Rhodes refused to let the pandemic ruin her 80th birthday celebrations at the weekend.</p>

<p>‘I’ve been managing to have my friends over in groups of five,’ the pink-haired Zandra tells me, referring to the ‘rule of six’. She says: ‘It worked out really well. My age is moving, but I don’t feel old.’</p>
